@AuthorizationToken = {{token}}
@baseUrl = {{host}}

### OBTENER GRUPOS
@id=1
GET {{baseUrl}}/grupos HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}

### OBTENER GRUPOS FILTRADOS
@id=1
GET {{baseUrl}}/grupos HTTP/1.1
    ?query=
    &order[nombre]=desc
    &page=1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}


### OBTENER UN GRUPO
@id=1
GET {{baseUrl}}/grupos/{{id}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}


### NUEVO GRUPO

POST {{baseUrl}}/grupos HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Test23",
  "estadoId": 1,
  "modo": "U",
  "usuarios": [
  		"/api/usuarios/1"
  ]
}

